Pre-Game Insights: Azerbaijan and Sweden will meet for a UEFA Nations League C clash in Baku on Thursday evening.
Azerbaijan enjoyed four friendly clashes in 2024, only losing one.
Sweden finished in third position in their section with 10 points during the 2022-23 UEFA Nations League.
Jon Dahl Tomasson is now tasked with guiding Azerbaijan to Nations League glory and World Cup qualification next year.
Sweden boasts some of the finest names in League C of this year's Nations League.
